<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Lorah Njuguna — Web Developer & Digital Builder</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --forest: #1C3A2A; --cream: #F5ECD7; --cream-dark: #EDE0C4;
    --camel: #C19A6B; --toffee: #8B6332; --ink: #0F1F17;
    --muted-light: #7A6A52; --muted-dark: rgba(245,236,215,0.55); --white: #FDFAF4;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }

  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1.2rem 4rem; background: rgba(28,58,42,0.96); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(193,154,107,0.15); }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--camel); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--muted-dark); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--camel); }

  .hero { min-height: 100vh; background: var(--forest); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center; padding: 8rem 4rem 5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px; width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(193,154,107,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%); pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-text { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-status { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; background: rgba(193,154,107,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(193,154,107,0.25); color: var(--camel); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .status-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ADE80; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  .hero h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 6rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.1s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--camel); }
  .hero-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted-dark); max-width: 440px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.2s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.3s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--toffee); color: var(--cream); padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0.03em; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #7A5629; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--cream); padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border: 1px solid rgba(245,236,215,0.25); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0.03em; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--camel); color: var(--camel); }
  .hero-right { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; animation: fadeLeft 0.9s 0.3s ease forwards; opacity: 0; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-info-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(193,154,107,0.2); padding: 2.5rem; width: 340px; }
  .info-label { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--camel); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0.9rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(193,154,107,0.1); }
  .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-key { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted-dark); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .info-val { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--cream); font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }
  .info-val.green { color: #4ADE80; }

  section { padding: 6rem 4rem; }
  .section-label { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--toffee); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink); }
  .section-sub { color: var(--muted-light); max-width: 520px; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .dark-section { background: var(--forest); color: var(--cream); }
  .dark-section .section-label { color: var(--camel); }
  .dark-section .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .dark-section .section-sub { color: var(--muted-dark); }

  #services { background: var(--white); }
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(139,99,50,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.12); }
  .service-card { background: var(--white); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .service-card:hover { background: var(--cream); }
  .service-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--toffee); transition: width 0.35s ease; }
  .service-card:hover::after { width: 100%; }
  .service-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(139,99,50,0.08); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
  .service-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted-light); line-height: 1.75; }

  #process { background: var(--cream-dark); }
  .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem; }
  .process-step { position: relative; }
  .step-line { width: 100%; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--toffee), rgba(193,154,107,0.2)); margin-bottom: 2rem; position: relative; }
  .step-line::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: -4px; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--toffee); }
  .step-num { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--toffee); letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .process-step h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .process-step p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted-light); line-height: 1.75; }

  #portfolio { background: var(--white); }
  .work-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .work-card { border: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.12); overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s; background: var(--white); }
  .work-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(28,58,42,0.1); }
  .work-thumb { height: 200px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
  .work-thumb img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top; transition: transform 0.4s ease; display: block; }
  .work-card:hover .work-thumb img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .work-niche { position: absolute; top: 1rem; left: 1rem; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45); color: #fff; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.28rem 0.6rem; z-index: 2; }
  .work-status { position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1rem; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 0.28rem 0.6rem; z-index: 2; }
  .work-status.live { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.2); color: #4ADE80; }
  .work-status.dev { background: rgba(193,154,107,0.2); color: var(--camel); }
  .work-info { padding: 1.6rem; }
  .work-info h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .work-info p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted-light); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .work-link { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--toffee); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.3); padding-bottom: 0.1rem; transition: color 0.2s; display: inline-block; }
  .work-link:hover { color: var(--forest); }
  .work-link.coming { color: var(--muted-light); border-color: transparent; cursor: default; }
  .work-card.featured { grid-column: span 2; }
  .work-card.featured .work-thumb { height: 240px; }

  #pricing { background: var(--cream-dark); }
  .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; align-items: start; }
  .pricing-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.12); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
  .pricing-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(28,58,42,0.08); }
  .pricing-card.featured { background: var(--forest); border-color: var(--toffee); color: var(--cream); transform: scale(1.03); }
  .pricing-card.featured:hover { transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-4px); }
  .pricing-popular { display: inline-block; background: var(--toffee); color: var(--cream); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.28rem 0.7rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .pricing-tier { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--muted-light); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pricing-card.featured .pricing-tier { color: var(--muted-dark); }
  .pricing-amount { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--toffee); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .pricing-currency { font-size: 1.1rem; vertical-align: super; }
  .pricing-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted-light); margin-bottom: 1.8rem; line-height: 1.65; }
  .pricing-card.featured .pricing-desc { color: var(--muted-dark); }
  .pricing-features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .pricing-features li { font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.55rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.08); display: flex; gap: 0.7rem; align-items: flex-start; color: var(--ink); }
  .pricing-card.featured .pricing-features li { color: rgba(245,236,215,0.8); border-color: rgba(193,154,107,0.1); }
  .pricing-features li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--toffee); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.15rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .btn-pricing { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 0.9rem; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; border: 1.5px solid var(--toffee); color: var(--toffee); transition: all 0.2s; }
  .btn-pricing:hover { background: var(--toffee); color: var(--cream); }
  .pricing-card.featured .btn-pricing { background: var(--toffee); color: var(--cream); }
  .pricing-card.featured .btn-pricing:hover { background: #7A5629; }
  .pricing-note { text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted-light); margin-top: 2rem; font-style: italic; }

  #stack { background: var(--white); }
  .stack-wrap { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .stack-pill { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 1.1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.2); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink); background: var(--cream); transition: all 0.2s; }
  .stack-pill:hover { background: var(--forest); color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--forest); }
  .stack-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--toffee); flex-shrink: 0; }

  #about { background: var(--forest); color: var(--cream); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-body { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted-dark); line-height: 1.9; }
  .about-body p + p { margin-top: 1.2rem; }
  .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .about-stat strong { display: block; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--camel); line-height: 1; }
  .about-stat span { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted-dark); margin-top: 0.4rem; display: block; }

  #contact { background: var(--cream-dark); }
  .contact-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .contact-inner .section-title { color: var(--forest); }
  .contact-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid rgba(139,99,50,0.15); padding: 3.5rem; position: relative; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .contact-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 3rem; right: 3rem; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--toffee), var(--camel)); }
  .contact-card p { color: var(--muted-light); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .contact-email {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--forest);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--toffee);
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-email:hover { color: var(--toffee); }
  .contact-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--toffee);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-cta:hover { background: #7A5629; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  footer { background: var(--ink); color: rgba(245,236,215,0.35); padding: 2rem 4rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes fadeLeft { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); } }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.5; } }
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; } .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem; } .hero-right { display: none; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .work-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .work-card.featured { grid-column: span 1; }
    .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .pricing-card.featured { transform: none; }
    #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; } .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .contact-card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#">Lorah<span>.</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#portfolio">Work</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-status"><span class="status-dot"></span>Available for new projects · Nairobi, Kenya</div>
    <h1>Websites that<br/><em>work</em> for your<br/>business</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Web developer and digital builder based in Nairobi. I design and build e-commerce stores, landing pages, and web platforms for businesses across Kenya — fast, clean, and built to convert.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Start a Project</a>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn-ghost">See My Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-info-card">
      <div class="info-label">// Developer Profile</div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-key">LOCATION</span><span class="info-val">Nairobi, Kenya 🇰🇪</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-key">SPECIALITY</span><span class="info-val">Web Development</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-key">STACK</span><span class="info-val">React · Supabase · Netlify</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-key">TURNAROUND</span><span class="info-val">1–3 weeks</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-key">STATUS</span><span class="info-val green">● Accepting Projects</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="services">
  <div class="section-label">What I do</div>
  <div class="section-title">Services</div>
  <p class="section-sub">End-to-end website development for businesses that want a strong, professional online presence.</p>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">01</div><div class="service-icon">🛒</div><h3>E-Commerce Stores</h3><p>Full online shops with product listings, mobile-friendly checkout, and M-Pesa & card payment integration.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">02</div><div class="service-icon">🚀</div><h3>Landing Pages</h3><p>High-converting single-page sites for launches, services, and lead generation. Fast, impressive, mobile-optimised.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">03</div><div class="service-icon">🌐</div><h3>Business Websites</h3><p>Multi-page professional sites with services, portfolio, blog, and contact. A digital home your business can be proud of.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">04</div><div class="service-icon">⚙️</div><h3>Web App Builds</h3><p>Interactive platforms — dashboards, booking systems, community tools — built to scale.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">05</div><div class="service-icon">🔧</div><h3>Fixes & Revamps</h3><p>Outdated or broken site? Speed improvements, mobile fixes, full redesigns — all handled.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card reveal"><div class="service-num">06</div><div class="service-icon">📦</div><h3>Hosting & Deployment</h3><p>Domain setup, Netlify, Vercel, and Cloudflare Pages. I get your site live and keep it running.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="process">
  <div class="section-label">How I work</div>
  <div class="section-title">From Brief to Live Site</div>
  <p class="section-sub">A clear, transparent process — you always know where your project stands.</p>
  <div class="process-grid">
    <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">01 / Discovery</div><h3>We Talk</h3><p>I learn about your business, goals, audience, and timeline. The right questions upfront mean nothing gets missed.</p></div>
    <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">02 / Proposal</div><h3>Clear Quote</h3><p>A fixed price and scope of work within 24 hours. No vague estimates — just an honest number.</p></div>
    <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">03 / Build</div><h3>We Build</h3><p>I build and share a preview link. Two rounds of revisions included to get every detail right.</p></div>
    <div class="process-step reveal"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">04 / Launch</div><h3>Go Live</h3><p>Your site goes live. I handle deployment, test everything, and walk you through it.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="portfolio">
  <div class="section-label">Selected Work</div>
  <div class="section-title">Projects I've Built</div>
  <p class="section-sub">Real sites across e-commerce, professional services, beauty, food & beverage, and EdTech.</p>
  <div class="work-grid">

    <div class="work-card reveal">
      <div class="work-thumb">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Tibah Treats"/>
        <div class="work-niche">E-Commerce</div><div class="work-status live">● Live</div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-info">
        <h3>Tibah Treats</h3>
        <p>Cookie e-commerce store with product catalogue, KSh pricing, and M-Pesa payment instructions.</p>
        <a href="https://tibahtreats.co.ke" target="_blank" class="work-link">tibahtreats.co.ke →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="work-card reveal">
      <div class="work-thumb">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Njoroge & Associates"/>
        <div class="work-niche">Professional Services</div><div class="work-status live">● Live</div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-info">
        <h3>Njoroge & Associates</h3>
        <p>Premium law firm landing page. Dark navy, gold accents, practice areas and consultation booking.</p>
        <a href="https://njoroge-and-advocates.lwn.workers.dev" target="_blank" class="work-link">View Site →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="work-card reveal">
